  "title": "In Vila Planalto-DF, six people sighted a large round UFO [1993]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/04/in-vila-planalto-df-six-people-sighted-a-large-round-ufo-1993/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1oZ",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>OCT 9th, 1993</strong>. Time: 20:00. Duration: 15 minutes. Six people in Vila Planalto, Brasília, Distrito Federal, observed for fifteen minutes a large, round UFO, with red, yellow and green colors, flying at low altitude and slow speed. According to the witnesses, the unknown object made a vertical trajectory south of Vila Planalto, and 2 km away from the observer. The sighting took place under good visibility conditions and was carried out with the naked eye</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.349. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Vila Planalto, Brasília, Distrito Federal</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
